item.description:
Since noone seems to be much interested in coming over to watch the Celtics, maybe we should venture out to the Princeton Station?  One of our favorite groups is playing "four on the floor" to some good ole fashion Rock 'n Roll.

If anyone gets there before me, (I'll try and be there for 7pm), then try and get a big table.  I think we'll have more takers for this than the Celtics game, and it'll be on the TV anyway.

Sorry for the last minute and "can't make up my mind" type thingee, but I would like to "cut a rug" a little tonight ;)

SUZ
item.how_to_find_us: first come first serve, whoever gets there first grab a table...
item.name: Shall we try the Princeton Station at 7pm?? 4 on the floor is playing!
